<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
<p>Last updated: July 2026</p>
<p>DropPost runs locally on the account owner's own computer. It does not transmit data to any third-party server other than Instagram's and TikTok's own APIs, which it uses solely to publish scheduled content.</p>
<p>Access tokens are stored encrypted, locally, on the user's device using the operating system's built-in credential protection. No data is collected, sold, or shared with any other party.</p>
<p>The account owner may disconnect any connected account at any time, which removes the stored token from the device.</p>
